---
import SectionHeader from '../../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
import Button from '../../ui/Button.astro';
import { TRAINING_DAILY_SCHEDULE } from '../../../constants/trainingScheduleConstants';
import { ROUTE_CONTACT, ROUTE_PAYMENT } from '../../../constants/routesConstants';
---
<section id="DailySchedule" class="m-10  font-bold">
  <SectionHeader title="Daily Schedule for 200 hrs YTTC" />
 
  <div class="flex flex-col w-full md:flex-row">
  <div class="space-y-6 mt-6 w-full md:w-1/3">
    {TRAINING_DAILY_SCHEDULE.slice(0,4).map(({ time, activity }) => (
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-full bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 skew-x-[-5deg] flex justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block skew-x-[5deg] font-bold">{time}</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">{activity}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <div class="border border-black rounded-lg p-6 mt-10 md:mt-0 my-5 w-full md:w-1/3 text-center">
    <h3 class="font-bold">Daily Schedule for 200 hrs YTTC
</h3>
   <p class="mt-4 ">
    A well-structured daily routine forms the backbone of yoga courses, especially intensive programs like the 200 hour Yoga Teacher Training (YTT). This carefully organized schedule ensures effective learning, fosters discipline, and helps students seamlessly incorporate yogic principles into their daily lives. By maintaining a balanced schedule, students stay refreshed, energized, and focused throughout the day.
  </p>
  <h4 class="mt-6 font-semibold">Weekly Schedule: Monday to Saturday</h4>
  <img src="/yogacoursepic.jpg" alt="Yoga Daily Schedule" class="w-full rounded-lg mt-4" />
  <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
    <Button href={ROUTE_CONTACT} class="border border-red-600 text-red-600 px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-red-50">Book Course</Button>
    <Button href={ROUTE_PAYMENT} class="border border-red-600 text-red-600 px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-red-50">Pay Course</Button>
  </div>
  </div>
    <div class=" w-full md:w-1/3">
   {TRAINING_DAILY_SCHEDULE.slice(4,).map(({ time, activity }) => (
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-full bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 skew-x-[-5deg] flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block skew-x-[5deg] font-bold">{time}</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">{activity}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
